# Rule 4: Analytics & Monitoring

## Core Principle

Analytics are a **cross-cutting concern** integrating throughout the trading pipeline. All analytics must support **real-time processing**, **batch analytics**, **regime awareness**, and **multi-timeframe capabilities**.

---

## Analytics Integration Points

```
RULE 2: DATA PIPELINE (Phases 1-5)
├── Pre-Trade Analytics
│   ├── Signal Quality Assessment
│   ├── Liquidity Analysis
│   └── Risk Metrics Calculation

RULE 3: RISK GOVERNANCE (Phases 6-10)
├── Risk Analytics
│   ├── VaR Calculation
│   ├── Position Risk Assessment
