## IAnalyticsComponent Interface

```python
class IAnalyticsComponent(ISystemComponent):
    @abstractmethod
    async def process_real_time_data(self, data: Dict[str, Any]) -> Dict[str, Any]:
        """Process real-time market data or trading events"""
        pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def process_batch_data(self, data: pd.DataFrame, start: datetime, end: datetime) -> Dict:
        """Process historical data in batch mode"""
        pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def get_regime_aware_metrics(self, regime_context: Dict) -> Dict[str, Any]:
        """Get metrics adjusted for current market regime"""
        pass
    
    @abstractmethod
    async def get_multi_timeframe_analysis(self, timeframes: List[str]) -> Dict[str, Dict]:
        """Get analysis across multiple timeframes"""
        pass
```

