## Regime-Aware Analytics

### Regime Adjustments

| Volatility Regime | Risk Multiplier | Confidence Threshold | Position Sizing |
|-------------------|-----------------|---------------------|-----------------|
| Low | 1.2 | 0.50 | 1.1x |
| Normal | 1.0 | 0.60 | 1.0x |
| High | 0.7 | 0.70 | 0.8x |
| Extreme | 0.4 | 0.80 | 0.5x |

```python
async def get_regime_aware_metrics(self, regime_context: Dict) -> Dict:
    volatility_regime = regime_context.get('volatility_regime')
    
    return {
        'current_regime': regime_context['primary_regime'],
        'regime_adjustments': REGIME_ADJUSTMENTS[volatility_regime],
        'expected_persistence': self._calculate_regime_persistence()
    }
```

