## MANDATORY Requirements

1. **ISystemComponent:** All analytics implement enhanced interface
2. **Real-Time:** Support streaming and event-driven processing
3. **Batch:** Support historical analysis and backtesting
4. **Attribution:** Provide strategy-level and factor-based attribution
5. **Regime Awareness:** Adapt to market regime conditions
6. **Multi-Timeframe:** Analyze across timeframes with correlation

---

## PROHIBITED Patterns

| Pattern | Violation |
|---------|-----------|
| Isolated analytics | Must integrate with regime engine |
| Single timeframe only | Must support multi-timeframe |
| Batch-only processing | Must support real-time |
| Non-attributed performance | Must provide attribution |
| Static risk models | Must adapt to regime changes |

